                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <h3>Learning Phase</h3>
                    <p>First 3 sessions build your unique behavioral profile</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <h3>Continuous Monitoring</h3>
                    <p>System tracks your behavior in real-time during each session</p>
                </div>
